## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ae731-103">다음 형식 라이브러리에서 `OLE_COLOR` 별칭인 `int`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ae731-103">In the following type library,  `OLE_COLOR` is an alias for `int`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ae731-104">인수를 가져오는 동안 합니다 `Color` 접근자로 표시 됩니다는 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComAliasNameAttribute> 그들에 게 해당 형식 라이브러리 참조를 나타내려면 `OLE_COLOR`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ae731-104">During import, the arguments of the `Color` accessor are marked with the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComAliasNameAttribute> to indicate that type library refers to them as `OLE_COLOR`.</span></span>  
  
```  
  
typedef int OLE_COLOR;    
  
interface Baz {  
 HRESULT SetColor([in] OLE_COLOR cl);  
 HRESULT GetColor([out, retval] OLE_COLOR *cl);  
}  
  
```  
  
